reviews.text:
Great choices for having lunch near temple.

I order the menu as pictures but cannot remember what it call.

The one with green vegetable is simply but delicious with smell of garlic.

The fried tofu is good.
I will choose the available alternatives as long as they still exist.
The best is the chicken rice.
Foid is ok
Friendly owner, great character, must stop place for an easy lunch after a morning bike ride
